    "key": "The main label on this elixir is illegible, written in hastily scrawled sigils in some foreign or fake language. Underneath, written in a tidy, small script: 'SIDE EFFECTS: MANY'. Thrilling!",
    "original": "The main label on this elixir is illegible, written in hastily scrawled sigils in some foreign or fake language. Underneath, written in a tidy, small script: 'SIDE EFFECTS: MANY'. Thrilling!",
